headline: Should You Rethink Paychex After Its 19% Decline in 2025?
summary: Wondering if Paychex is a hidden bargain or trading above its worth? You are not alone, as plenty of investors are keeping an eye out for standout value among HR and payroll service providers. The stock has experienced some turbulence, holding steady over the last week but sliding 12.1% in the past month and down 19.1% year to date.
